Celtic Outfitters: Celtic Outfitters is an Irish-themed online retailer located in Arkadelphia, Arkansas, USA. Celtic Outfitters is a family owned and operated business which was established in 1996. The original store was located in downtown Arkadelphia, Arkansas, but in 2013, the store relocated to a much larger facility on Highway 8, in Arkadelphia, Arkansas. Celtic Outfitters carries a wide range of high quality Irish products including, jewelry, clothing, and gifts. They also have on staff, a professional jewelry maker who can create custom jewelry for customers.
